            <note xml:id="n17071608" n="8">Here 
        <name type="person" key="Clark, William">Clark</name>begins a practice he often followed
        subsequently, of placing several days' courses and distances together. He originally
        misdated these courses July 15, 16, 17, and 18, then corrected by writing over. Part of
        the courses for July 17 are included, although that date is not in the heading as
        corrected. There is a gap of most of a page between the end of the July 16 entry and the
        start of these courses. 
        <name type="person" key="Clark, William">Clark</name>may have written the courses of these
        four days first and left space to insert the narrative entries later. The July 17 entry
